angelist is regularly referred to as <i>Matthew</i>, while the apostle chosen to replace Judas Iscariot is distinguished as   Matthias .  A related name from the same Hebrew roots, but reversed, is   Jonathan .  Throughout the English-speaking world <i>Matthew</i> has been particularly popular since the 1970s."],"variants":[{"name":"Mathew","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Matthew ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir Matthew Worlington, Knight was born in 1255, in England, United Kingdom, his father, William Worlington, was 16 and his mother, Sarah Hatch, was 16. He had at least 1 daughter with Sara."},"et":{"1255–":"1255–Surnud","1255–Male":"1255–Surnud","1260–Female":"1260–Surnud","1270–1351":"1270–1351","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1240–Female":"1240–Surnud","about 1270":"umbes 1270","1255":"1255","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1255–":"1255–Kuollut","1255–Male":"1255–Kuollut","1260–Female":"1260–Kuollut","1270–1351":"1270–1351","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1240–Female":"1240–Kuollut","about 1270":"noin 1270","1255":"1255","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1255–":"1255–Décédé","1255–Male":"1255–Décédé","1260–Female":"1260–Décédée","1270–1351":"1270–1351","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","1240–Female":"1240–Décédée","about 1270":"environ 1270","1255":"1255","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir Matthew Worlington, Knight est né en 1255, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, William Worlington, avait 16 ans et sa mère, Sarah Hatch, avait 16 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Sara."},"de":{"1255–":"1255–Verstorben","1255–Male":"1255–Verstorben","1260–Female":"1260–Verstorben","1270–1351":"1